articles.author: Helen Regan, Isaac Yee, Eve Brennan
articles.title: Australian teens among six tourists dead as countries warn of suspected methanol poisonings in Laos - CNN
articles.description: An Australian teenager has become the sixth foreign tourist to die in a suspected mass methanol poisoning in Laos, as a growing list of countries warned of the potentially fatal consequences of drinking tainted alcohol in the Southeast Asian country.
